ðŸš€ Problem Statement: MERN Product CRUD App

Build a simple MERN application that allows users to perform CRUD operations on products.
No authentication required.

ðŸ“Œ Requirements

Each Product should have:

name (String)

price (Number)

description (String)

Implement following REST API routes:

Routes

Create Product

POST /api/products


Request Body: { name, price, description }

Response: Created product

Get All Products

GET /api/products


Response: List of all products

Update Product by ID

PUT /api/products/:id


Request Body: { name, price, description }

Response: Updated product

Delete Product by ID

DELETE /api/products/:id


Response: { message: "Product deleted" }
